


 what .js-lang can do on HTML-page in browser-envi?
 
 
 
  using browser provided APIs , can do any magic to HTML page.
  
  browser provided APIs
  
  e.g
  
     --> DOM ( Document Object Model )
   
   using DOM
   ------------
    --> can create,retrieve,update,delete HTML elements.
    --> can change element's attributes
    --> can change element's style
    --> can change element's text
    --> can change element's inner-content
    --> can listen events on Elements 
    --> can create rich UI components
    --> can validate form-fields before submit
    
    
    --> can communicate with server async, update results in page ( AJAX )